def slugify(text):
    # Convert to lowercase
    text = text.lower()

    text = re.sub(r'\s+', '-', text)

    text = re.sub(r'[^a-z0-9-]', '', text)
    return text

def slugify(text):

    text = text.strip().lower()  # Remove leading and trailing spaces and convert to lowercase
    text = re.sub(r'[\s]+', '-', text)  # Replace all spaces with hyphens
    return text
